Class SingleLinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • SingleLinkedList<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class SingleLinkedList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<E>
    SingleLinkedList is a class that provides some of the capabilities required by the List interface using a single linked list data structure. Only the following methods are provided: get, set, add, remove, size, toString
    Author:
    Furkan, Koffman and Wolfgang
